<subSubSection pageId="14" pageNumber="131" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1430,1998]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1430,1455]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">Description.</emphasis>
Body (
<figureCitation box="[379,443,1431,1455]" captionStart="FIGURE 1. a – d" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1253,1276]" captionTargetBox="[195,1386,213,1213]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[178,1409,193,1232]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 1. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida? aculeiformis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida) apicispina Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – q. Kapsa (Rigida? explanata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222871/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[431,443,1431,1455]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="1.0">
<date box="[431,443,1431,1455]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">1</date>
</number>
</figureCitation>
i, j) sordid yellow. Coronal suture (
<figureCitation box="[836,898,1431,1455]" captionStart="FIGURE 1. a – d" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1253,1276]" captionTargetBox="[195,1386,213,1213]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[178,1409,193,1232]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 1. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida? aculeiformis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida) apicispina Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – q. Kapsa (Rigida? explanata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222871/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[888,898,1431,1455]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
k) short, not reaching midlength of vertex. Face (
<figureCitation box="[159,223,1467,1491]" captionStart="FIGURE 1. a – d" captionStartId="7.[151,250,1253,1276]" captionTargetBox="[195,1386,213,1213]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[178,1409,193,1232]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURE 1. a – d. Kapsa (Rigida? aculeiformis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; e – h. Kapsa (Rigida) apicispina Yang &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; i – l. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov.; m – q. Kapsa (Rigida? explanata Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222871/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[212,223,1467,1491]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="1.0">1</number>
</figureCitation>
l) long.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1430,1998]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Abdominal apodemes broad but short, extended to the hind margin of the 
<number box="[1059,1073,1506,1530]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="3.0">3</number>
rd sternite. Anal tube appendage (
<figureCitation box="[159,224,1542,1566]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[212,224,1542,1566]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
a–c) tapering apically, apex curved laterally from hind view.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1430,1998]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Pygofer dorsal appendage (
<figureCitation box="[508,574,1578,1602]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[562,574,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
a–c) falcate, basal 
<number box="[788,802,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="2.0">2</number>
/ 
<number box="[811,823,1578,1602]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="3.0">3</number>
slim, pointed apically and curved ventrad. Subgenital plate (
<figureCitation box="[221,286,1614,1638]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[272,286,1614,1638]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
a, e) with 
<number box="[398,412,1614,1638]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="4.0">4</number>
lateral macrosetae, peglike microsetae of basal group comparatively longer. Paramere (
<figureCitation captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[151,164,1650,1674]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
f) with apical part relatively short, preapical lobe small. Connective (
<figureCitation box="[942,1007,1650,1674]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<quantity box="[994,1007,1650,1674]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="8.0" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" unit="g" value="8.0">8</quantity>
</figureCitation>
g) with lateral arms short, manubrium long. Aedeagus shaft (
<figureCitation box="[412,481,1686,1710]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1009,1032]" captionTargetBox="[192,1399,208,977]" captionTargetId="figure@15.[177,1409,195,987]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 8. Kapsa (Rigida) brevis Cao &amp; Zhang sp. nov. a. genital capsule; b. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, lateral view; c. pygofer dorsal appendage and anal tube appendage, hind view; d. subgenital plate, paramere, connective and the 9 th sternite, dorsal view; e. subgenital plate, dorsal view; f. paramere, lateral view; g. connective; h. aedeagus, lateral view; i. aedeagus, ventral view." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/222878/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
Fig. 
<number box="[468,481,1686,1710]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131" value="8.0">8</number>
</figureCitation>
h, i) tubular, denticulate on distal half, dorsal apodeme large, basal process small; gonopore terminal, ventral.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1430,1998]" box="[199,688,1758,1782]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,371,1758,1782]" pageId="14" pageNumber="131">Measurement.</emphasis>
